<L>__{132. in the rigging night}
<A>__{midshipmen calamy rye and boyle are eating from a bag of broken biscuits ('ships nuts') as they sit perched up in the rigging. on seeing jack, they break into their own song.}
<C>__{midshipmen}
<D>__{our captain was very good to us. he dipped his prick in phosphorus. it shed a light all through the night. and steered us through the bosphorus.}
